data.name: Business Overdraft
data.description: A Business Overdraft from MyState Bank can give you access to additional funds when you need it most for any worthwhile business purpose. Your MyState Bank Business Overdraft can be linked to a business banking transaction account to provide you with more flexibility to manage your funds on a daily basis. This overdraft facility can also be conveniently accessed and managed via Phone and Internet Banking, free ATM access, EFTPOS and at any of our branches.

features.additionalInfo: Only pay interest on the money you use.
A Business Overdraft from MyState Bank can give you access to additional funds when you need it most for any worthwhile business purpose.
Access your overdraft via internet and phone banking, ATM, EFTPOS and cheque.

eligibility.additionalInfo: Available wholly or predominantly for business purposes operating in Australia.

lendingRates.additionalInfo: Customer interest rate margins may also apply to the rates quoted.Full interest rate details are available on application.
